{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clown Town is an immersive <strong>horror</strong> exploration game. Make your way through a <strong><i>massive abandoned circus</i></strong> filled with <strong>psychotic</strong> clowns and <strong>demonic</strong> entities. Intensity amplifies as you make it deeper into the levels. Can you <strong><i>survive</i></strong>?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Intense Gameplay Mechanics</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sprint through the darkness</strong> to answer phones, repair the electricity, or hold a demon child to prevent it from crying.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Terrifying Levels</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Chill-inducing</strong> ambiance combined with <strong>unpredictable</strong> enemies. The levels get larger and more challenging the further you go.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Deep Immersion\u00a0</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Retro</strong> graphics, minimal UI, hear your own <strong>heart beat</strong> as death approaches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Psychotic Clowns</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Many enemies with unique behaviors, they stalk you through the darkness, whisper into your ears, and chase you at a\u00a0<strong>horrifying </strong>pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3520480?t=1739641431","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3520480?t=1739641431","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520480/85c827516ce252c67b0677f28c889c36b62e1ac8/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739641431","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3520480/85c827516ce252c67b0677f28c8